The paper is about proposing a new quantum-safe asymmetric cryptosystem, which falls under the category of cryptography (cs.CR). The paper also involves analyzing the security of the new cryptosystem, which involves information theory (cs.IT) and complexity theory (cs.CC). The use of extra superincreasing sequences and anomalous subset sums suggests that the paper may also fall under the categories of computational complexity (cs.CE) and machine learning (cs.LG).
